title: AUDIO OF KEY VERSES OF THE HOLY QURAN & HOLY BIBLE
description:
AUDIO OF KEY VERSES OF THE HOLY QURAN & HOLY BIBLE

YHWH! YHWH ANGEL GABRIEL! YHWH ANGEL MICHAEL! YHWH MESSIAH JESUS CHRIST!

Jerusalem (AFP) - Tens of thousands of Jewish worshippers massed at Jerusalem's Western Wall on Wednesday as part of celebrations for the Sukkot holiday, organisers said, while tensions in the area diminished.

QURAN 48:19-21
And many gains will they acquire (besides): and Allah/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY is Exalted in Power, Full of Wisdom.

And many gains which they will acquire. And ever is Allah/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY Exalted in Might and Wise.

Allah/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY  has promised you many gains that you will take [in the future] and has hastened for you this [victory] and withheld the hands of people from you - that it may be a sign for the believers and [that] He may guide you to a straight path.

And [He [ALLAH/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY] promises] other [victories] that you were [so far] unable to [realize] which Allah [ALLAH/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY] has already encompassed. And ever is Allah , over all things, competent.

QURAN 7:128
Sahih International
Said Moses to his people, "Seek help through Allah/YHWH/HEAVENLY FATHER GOD ALMIGHTY and be patient. Indeed, the earth belongs to Allah . He causes to inherit it whom He wills of His servants. And the [best] outcome is for the righteous."
